Rules for RANIAG Laravel 11 Project:

- Use Laravel 11 conventions only
- Use Blade + Bootstrap 5 only
- Do NOT use React
- Do NOT use Vue
- Do NOT modify vendor files
- Do NOT rewrite .env automatically
- Use MVC architecture
- Use service classes for business logic
- Use repository pattern only when needed
- Use migrations properly
- Use Eloquent relationships
- Follow RESTful controller structure
- Separate Admin and Agency controllers
- Keep public reporting routes separate
- Use Form Request validation
- Use middleware for RBAC
- Use clean code principles
- Avoid duplicate logic
- Ask before installing additional packages
- Never regenerate existing migrations